summary 'Add automatic integration tests to your puppet runs.'
description 'This module was written to allow you to include integration tests as part of your puppet runs.
* Integration tests will automatically run at the end of a puppet run.
* They will only run if the puppet run contained changes.
* .. or failed last time.
* Cucumber tests will be support first but other providers could be added (such as server spec tests)

This module is presently in development, any questions or suggestions, please contact dave@practicalclouds.com'

project_page 'http://www.practicalclouds.com/content/guide/pclouds-integrate-integration-tests-for-puppet-runs'

